ore reports first cases of local transmission; 4 out of 6 new cases did not travel to China| url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/coronavirus-spore-reports-first-cases-of-local-transmission-4-out-of-6-new-cases-did-not| vauthors=Khalik S| date=4 February 2020| access-date=5 February 2020| newspaper=[[The Straits Times]]|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200204101450/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/coronavirus-spore-reports-first-cases-of-local-transmission-4-out-of-6-new-cases-did-not| archive-date=4 February 2020| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"STAT-Severity\">{{cite news|url=https://www.statnews.com/2020/01/30/limited-data-may-skew-assumptions-severity-coronavirus-outbreak/ |title=Limited data on coronavirus may be skewing assumptions about severity|vauthors=Branswell H|date=30 January 2020|publisher=[[Stat (website)|STAT]]|access-date=13 March 2020|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200201161634/https://www.statnews.com/2020/01/30/limited-data-may-skew-assumptions-severity-coronavirus-outbreak/ |archive-date=1 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SunChinaAfrica\">{{cite news| title=Coronavirus: China to repay Africa in safeguarding public health| url=https://www.sunnewsonline.com/coronavirus-china-to-repay-africa-in-safeguarding-public-health/| vauthors=Paulinus A| date=25 February 2020| access-date=10 March 2020| newspaper=[[The Sun (Nigeria)|The Sun]]| url-status=live| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200309103243/https://www.sunnewsonline.com/coronavirus-china-to-repay-africa-in-safeguarding-public-health/| archive-date=9 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"TelegraphPangolins\">{{cite news |newspaper=The Telegraph |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/science/2016/03/15/pangolins-13-facts-about-the-worlds-most-hunted-animal/ |vauthors=Kelly G |date=1 January 2015|title=Pangolins: 13 facts about the world's most hunted animal |access-date=9 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191224153802