rs and Merchants in Bourbon Mexico, 1763-1810 |url=https://archive.org/details/minersmerchantsi0000brad |url-access=registration |location=New York |publisher=Cambridge University |date=1971 |isbn=978-0521102070 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Braudel |first=Fernand |title=Civilization and Capitalism, 15th-18th century |volume=3 volumes |date=1984 |publisher=Collins |location=London |orig-year=1979 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Brown |first1=Jonathan |last2=Elliott |first2=John Huxtable |year=1980 |title=A Palace for a King. The Buen Retiro and the Court of Philip IV |place=New Haven |publisher=Yale University Press |isbn=978-0-300-02507-1 |ref=harv |url-access=registration |url=https://archive.org/details/palaceforkingbue0000brow }}\n*{{cite book|last=Bushnell |first=Amy |title=The King's Coffer: Proprietors of the Spanish Florida Treasury 1565\u20131702 |year=1981 |publisher=University Presses of Florida |location=Gainesville, Florida |isbn=978-0-8130-0690-1 |ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book | last = Carrera Damas | first = Germ\u00e1n | title = Historia general de Am\u00e9rica Latina | language = Spanish | publisher = UNESCO | year = 1999 | isbn =978-92-3-303151-7  |url = https://books.google.com/books?id=Bq2DZpHvPkkC#v=onepage&q&f=true |ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book|last=Chipman|first=Donald E.|title=Moctezuma's Children: Aztec Royalty under Spanish Rule, 1520\u20131700|year=2005|publisher=University of Texas Press|location=Austin, Texas|isbn=978-0-292-78264-8|url=https://books.google.com/?id=nbp7AAAAQBAJ&pg=PT55&lpg=PT55&dq=factor+overseer+accountant+treasurer+spanish#v=onepage&q=factor%20overseer%20accountant%20treasurer%20spanish&f=false|edition=  Individual e-book (no page numbers)|accessdate=22 October 2013 |ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book | last = Diego-Fern\u00e1ndez Sotelo | first = Rafael | title = Las capitulaciones colombinas | language = Spanish | publisher = El Colegio de Michoac\u00e1n A.C. | year = 1987 | isbn = 978-968-7230-30-6 | url = https://books.google.com